channel.title: SecetMerchanter 1.2 | Easy to use | Made in Delphi! |
channel.description:
[center][size=13pt][b]SecetMerchanter 1.2[/b][/size] Program made by [b]Secet[/b]
Screenshot of setup: [img]http://www.secetweb.com/images/secetmerchanter1dot2.PNG[/img]
[size=12pt]Doesn't it look easy?[/size] [/center] [b][i] What does it offer?[/i] [/b]
[ul][li]5_systemwide_hotkeys. F1, F2, F3, F4, F5. Systemwide means that when you accidently haven't selected Runescape window and you press F5, it won't refresh the browser (would cause you to logout) since it's registered for my program. After exiting it unregisters those hotkeys so they are in normal use again.
[/li]
[li]It has 4 different typing speeds for your needs.
Slow - 100ms + Random 150ms Normal - 50ms + Random 100ms Fast - 25ms + Random 50ms Spam! - Almost instant!
[/li]
[li]You can select unique colors and effects on every message!
[/li]
[li]Minimizes when you press Start button! When you want to bring it back, just doubleclick logo on tray bar. (or right click for more options)
[/li]
[li]Automatic spammer with normal delay + Random delay! Color and effects included!
[/li]
[li]Option for Always on Top!
[/li]
[li]Disable/enable hotkeys when needed!
[/li]
[li]Very nice and handy calculator that quickly calculates item prices and so on!
[/li]
[li]'Clear All' buttons in every groupbox.
[/li]
[li]By pressing buttons "Add to manual spammer" or "Add to automatic spammer" in calculator, program will make you selling message with just one click!
[/li]
[li]Hiding options - By pressing buttons, you can hide those parts that you don't need right now!
[/li][/ul]
[b]Changelog:[/b]
[ul][li]v1.0 - First release[/li] [li]v1.1 - Some new functions, check it out ;)[/li] [li]v1.2 - Hiding options[/li][/ul]
[center][size=13pt]Download it [url=http://files.sneamia.net/SecetMerchanter1dot2.exe]HERE![/url][/size]
WARNING: DO NOT use any other download links except this one, or the program might be infected with Virus/Keylogger!
Also remember to visit [url=http://www.secetweb.com]http://www.secetweb.com[/url] for more cool stuff![/center]
